[AD/PR] SUGAR Coffee Culture Balm Stick & Hydrating Mist ☕️

☕️ COFFEE CULTURE CLEANSING BALM STICK
 
 • Perfect for on-the-move cleansing, the Coffee Culture Cleansing Balm Stick with its unique solid balm formula melts gently onto damp skin and effortlessly breaks down long-wear makeup, deep exfoliates and cleanses skin in just a few swipes!

• Follow it up with a water-based cleanser or a face wash, and your skin is ready to glow!

☕️COFFEE CULTURE HYDRATING MIST 

 • Packed with the goodness of anti-oxidant rich Coffea Arabica (coffee) seed extract and licorice, this skin energizing formula minimizes the appearance of pores, soothes and brightens dull, tired skin. It also contains an anti-aging ingredient called 'betaine', which deeply moisturizes, prevents wrinkles and improves your skin texture! 

• Pick this mist and add an extra shot of caffeine into your skincare regime!
